headline: Humana Repricing Risk As Medicare Advantage Update Meets Care Delivery Shift
summary: Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services has proposed a near zero increase in Medicare Advantage payments, affecting growth expectations for Humana and peers. Humana is expanding home-based cardiac rehabilitation through a broad partnership with Carda Health. The company is rolling out the athenaOne platform across CenterWell locations to streamline clinical workflows and patient care. Humana, traded as NYSE:HUM, is facing a meaningful reset in expectations after a period of weak share...
